## Limitations

The analysis is limited by the availability of sources and the subjective nature of historical interpretation. The concept of race and whiteness is inherently complex and varies across different contexts and time periods. Additionally, the reliance on online discussions and secondary sources may not capture the full academic rigor of peer-reviewed historical research. Further research could include primary sources and more diverse perspectives to provide a comprehensive understanding of this transformation.